short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows price history on the real estate site https://r.onliner.by/

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds additional block of information on price history of every apartment on the real estate site https://r.onliner.by/. Using this extension users can see how prices change and decide when the best time to buy real estate. This extension doesn't store or access any user information.
